in florida rep bill nelson a candidate for the democratic 
gubernatorial nomination opened his campaign by trying to blame 
gop gov bob martinez for the early release of a convict who later 
was charged with killing two police officers 
nelson quickly shelved the strategy after a rival democrat 
accused him of trying to willie hortonize the election and a 
