hance withdrew a confusing tv ad questioning the integrity of gop 
rival and eventual victor clayton williams 
some observers cited the hance incident as proof that negative 
ads dont pay but others argued the ads flaws had nothing to do 
with its tone 
theres good and bad effective and ineffective smart and 
dumb said squier if you do a dumb ad it will probably 
backfire on you 
while much of the texas mudslinging was done through television 
