person as well 
in california for example democratic attorney general john van 
de kamp turned his candidacy announcement into a tirade against 
primary opponent diane feinstein former mayor of san francisco 
van de kamp blasted feinsteins record on civil rights 
insurance the environment and womens issues and accused her of 
budget mismanagement that turned san francisco into the city that 
could not pay 
feinsteins surge past van de kamp meanwhile was largely 
attributed to early positive ads that discussed her experience 
and support for the death penalty 
other are taking the positive approach as well 
in florida martinez is touting his record on the environment 
martin has run a soft gettingtoknowyou spot in illinois and 
