on a road intersection about 20 yards from the commodore and 
luckily failed to go off said the police spokesman he cannot be 
named under standing regulations 
the spokesman said bomb disposal experts established that the 
explosives were set to detonate at 4 am but they could not 
determine why they did not go off 
