partys charter removing references to its marxist past the 
structure of the peoples democratic party of afghanistan remains 
leninist but over the last few years its ideology has begun to 
change from communist to nationalist 
free enterprise flourishes in kabul and the government has 
lately begun allowing stateowned enterprises such as ariana 
